This error is triggered only when the approver has requests to approve. If this option is empty of requests, the page loads at https://approvals.princeton.edu/my_approval_requests/. 

To replicate you will need to make yourself a delegate able to assume the role of a user that has pending requests to approve and visit https://approvals.princeton.edu/my_approval_requests/ when you are acting as that user.
